                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Gavio Primo a militis Arsulana Germanil<lb break="no" n="2"/>la cum quinque fili<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> coniugi incompa<lb break="no" n="3"/>rabili cum quo vixit an<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>is</abbr></expan> XXV <expan><abbr>sarcofag</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>ponendum curavit
